msgid ""
"Parameter estimates from the mediation model, organized by direct effects, "
"indirect effects, and total effects."
msgstr ""

msgid "Direct effects"
msgstr "Direkte Effekte"

msgid ""
"Direct effects of predictors on outcomes, bypassing all mediators (the c or "
"c' path). A significant direct effect indicates that the predictor "
"influences the outcome independently of the mediation pathway."
msgstr ""

msgid "Indirect effects"
msgstr "Indirekte Effekte"

msgid ""
"Indirect effects of predictors on outcomes transmitted through mediators. "
"Each indirect effect is the product of the path coefficients along the "
"mediation pathway (a × b). A significant indirect effect indicates that "
"mediation occurs through that pathway."
msgstr ""

msgid "Total Effects"
msgstr "Gesamte Effekte"

msgid ""
"Total effects combining the direct effect and all indirect effects for each "
"predictor-outcome pair. The total effect equals the sum of the direct and "
"indirect effects (c = c' + a × b)."
msgstr ""

msgid "Total indirect effects"
msgstr "Gesamte indirekte Effekte"

msgid ""
"Total indirect effects summed across all mediators for each predictor-"
"outcome pair. When there are multiple mediators, this gives the combined "
"strength of all indirect pathways."
msgstr ""

msgid "Residual covariances"
msgstr "Residualkovarianzen"

msgid ""
"Estimated residual covariances between endogenous variables (mediators and "
"outcomes). These represent shared variance not accounted for by the model's "
"directed paths."
msgstr ""

msgid "Path coefficients"
msgstr "Pfadkoeffizienten"

msgid ""
"Individual path coefficients in the mediation model. These include the a "
"paths (predictor to mediator) and b paths (mediator to outcome), which "
"constitute the building blocks of indirect effects."
msgstr ""

msgid "Estimator is %s."
msgstr "Schätzer ist %s."

msgid ""
"%1$s Not all bootstrap samples were successful: CI based on %2$.0f samples."
msgstr ""
"%1$s Nicht alle Bootstrap-Stichproben waren erfolgreich: KI basieren auf "
"%2$.0f Stichproben."

msgid ""
"Proportion of variance in each mediator and outcome variable explained by "
"its predictors in the mediation model."
msgstr ""

#, fuzzy
msgid "Path Plot"
msgstr "Pfaddiagramm"

msgid ""
"Visual representation of the mediation model showing predictors, mediators, "
"outcomes, directed paths, and (optionally) parameter estimates."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Currently it is not possible to plot mediation models with ordinal "
"variables. The plot could not be generated."
msgstr ""
"Derzeit ist es nicht möglich, Mediationsmodelle mit ordinalen Variablen "
"darzustellen. Das Diagramm konnte nicht erstellt werden."

msgid ""
"The plot could not be generated. The underlying code resulted in the "
"following error message: %s"
msgstr ""
"Das Diagramm konnte nicht erstellt werden. Der zugrunde liegende Code führte "
"zu folgender Fehlermeldung: %s"

